{"tid":1309372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［致攬炒爸打］關於眾籌，可否出個英文版介紹？","createTime":"2019-07-12T07:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T08:03:28.000Z","uid":227607,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a8f15a0eb139b64d541838547c8943ae8f7e1aa6","tid":1309372,"uid":227607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:22:24.000Z","msg":"致攬炒巴打，<br />\n<br />\n首先，好多謝你嘅無條件付出！<br />\n<br />\n話說我身邊有好多居港外籍人士都好關心呢次事件，但佢哋睇唔明中文。我有嘗試同佢地解釋，佢哋都好有興趣出分力，想捐錢。所以想問下可唔可以寫個用英文嘅介紹版本，以吸引更故港外籍人士關注！<br />\n<br />\n最後，請受小弟一拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1838d1e799caee956b99c1aa3fc1e92d30110bc0","tid":1309372,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:23:09.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n多語文版"},{"pid":"df78abb2a11e1532e003360e72d2d1ebfbd42edd","tid":1309372,"uid":26324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:23:38.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d198bd2bc1274012b58129d4749f1f7383e14d1c","tid":1309372,"uid":227607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:24:30.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講了"},{"pid":"1302f8f838651f8616e66f0c989d031657b3338d","tid":1309372,"uid":227607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:25:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5eadd529414e9734a8ceeb858a89717597b4705c","tid":1309372,"uid":227607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:27:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e8f8fd1abffe8092fa531139088adfc576b75224","tid":1309372,"uid":227607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:03:28.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}